snippet.title: Sprint 2 - (1976) - Arcade - gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Sprint 2 © 1976.   Kee Games.
[Coin-Op] Arcade Video Game

A review & playthrough of the historic Sprint 2.  The first mass-produced game from Atari (ie. Kee games) that used a microprocessor.   - Videogame history documentation project.
